<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٥٢٥ - ٥٥٢٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6085">مُسَدَّدٌ </a>: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةَ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4340">عَدِيٌّ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/895">الْبَرَاءِ</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3535">وَابْنِ أَبِي أَوْفَى </a><span class="special">﵃</span> قَالَا <span class="c2">«نَهَى النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَنْ لُحُومِ الْحُمُرِ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>